# AI-Driven Greeting API — Cursor rules

- Single source of truth for design: **`docs/README.md`** (English). Read before large changes.
- Stack: Java 25, Spring Boot 3.4.x, Maven. Do not downgrade Java without an ADR.
- DTOs: **Java records**. Wiring: **constructor injection only** (no `@Autowired` on fields).
- HTTP API: version prefix **`/v1/`**. Errors: **RFC 7807** via `@RestControllerAdvice`.
- Tests: follow **`docs/design/engineering.md`** (unit tests for `GreetingService`, integration for controller).
- Update OpenAPI / FDD / diagrams when you change public API or architecture boundaries.
